<h1 id="creating-a-layout">Creating a Layout</h1>
<p>Follow the steps as outlined and refer to the video below to add a new layout.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Click the Insert tab and select Layout.  Choose an appropriate page size. <em>Letter size is good for most maps in this class, only use the bigger ones if you are making a poster.</em></li>
</ul>

