<h1 id="export-your-map">Export Your Map</h1>

<p><strong>File Submission:</strong> Save the layout as a .pdf, name it <em>Kernel_Density.pdf</em>.  You will upload it to canvas.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Your map should look something like the map shown below. Different colors, element sizes, etc. are fine.  But it should have all the map elements listed above.</li>
</ul>

