<h1 id="save-your-project">Save your project.</h1>

<p>Click Save in the top left of the Arc Pro window.</p>
<ul>
  <li>If you are working on a Geography Department Lab computer, make sure to save your work the the H:/ drive and log off properly.  See the video of on the Lab Details page on canvas for a more detailed explanation.</li>
</ul>
